russtesha: There are subtitles available for this movie...
i cannot turn on subtitles- are there any???

Torrent is ok, movie works fine, quality good (good enough for me at least). Thanks for uploading and seeding.

The movie itself is an excellent Polish comedy. Quite old and not a high budget one, but the story and humour are hillarious.

Dzieki!

Unfortunately the audio and video drift gradually out of sync, and the English subtitles I found on opensubtitles.org go out of sync with both audio and video.  Frustrating!  Still, excellent movie and worth seeding if this is the only torrent out there.
